window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>As a child, Jackston Forbes made a promise to lovely - and pushy - Lizelle Menzies. </p> <p>A man of his word, Jackston never forgot that promise. Through the years of experience and growth, Jackston has become a powerful warrior, now returning to his home in the highlands to assume his place as his father's heir. </p> <p>But along the way he meets a young woman who will test the strength of his vow to marry Lizelle, and when he discovers the brutal and petty woman Lizelle has become, it becomes a difficult choice for him - will he remain true to a childhood vow or will he follow his heart? </p>"; 
